data.description: Beautifully remodeled Cape Cod w/stone front and three dormers! This 3-bedroom home has new flooring, fixtures, and all but two new windows throughout. The kitchen has new cabinets, counter tops, and backsplash. The attractive formal dining room flows into a spacious living room. Lovely arched doorways add a charming touch to the main level. There is one bedroom and a half bath on the main level. Hardwood floors under the vinyl plank flooring. Two bedrooms and a full bath w/double vanity on the upper level. Gas boiler heat. New roof, siding, chimney, and basement windows. 1-car garage, corner lot.
